{
  "name": "RPlog_Battle_Droid_Duel",
  "title": "Battle Droid Duel",
  "summary": "At a modified arena on Kalla, Arakyd Industries hosts a gladiatorial dueling-droids event drawing tens of thousands of spectators. The retired swoop racer Violet, settling into her seat with a bottle of brandy, befriends a Jawa named Lola while the warrior Siva watches from above. The star contestant is the modified 501-Z police droid Zed -- fighting as 'Shen-Lung' and serving as both droid and master -- who first survives a gauntlet of the arena's own deadly traps, dodging cleavers, impalers, and spinning blades before disabling them with his vibro-axes. He then faces the bulky Mark X Executioner, a flamethrower- and vibrosaw-armed killer droid, in a brutal melee. Zed's superior speed and twin axes shred the Mark X's chassis despite a few lucky blocks, and after a flurry of blows the Executioner short-circuits and collapses in smoke. Victorious and lightly charred, Zed exits to the workshop for repairs as cleaning droids clear the wreckage.",
